{"description":"PPAPI: Add FileIO::OpenDev for Map() and plugin-side writes\n\nBUG=253999,194304\n\nCommitted: https://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome?view=rev&revision=222726","cc":["chromium-reviews@chromium.org","yusukes+watch@chromium.org","raymes+watch@chromium.org","jam@chromium.org","yzshen+watch@chromium.org","joi+watch-content@chromium.org","darin-cc@chromium.org","sbc@chromium.org","piman+watch@chromium.org","binji@chromium.org","ihf+watch@chromium.org"],"reviewers":["bbudge@chromium.org","teravest@chromium.org"],"messages":[{"sender":"dmichael@chromium.org","recipients":["dmichael@chromium.org","bbudge@chromium.org","teravest@chromium.org","chromium-reviews@chromium.org","yusukes+watch@chromium.org","raymes+watch@chromium.org","jam@chromium.org","yzshen+watch@chromium.org","joi+watch-content@chromium.org","darin-cc@chromium.org","sbc@chromium.org","piman+watch@chromium.org","binji@chromium.org","ihf+watch@chromium.org"],"text":"I thought it would be good to split this off from Map/Unmap. This way we can also work on the plugin-side writes before quota enforcement in NaCl is ready.","disapproval":false,"date":"2013-09-05 22:20:42.640620","approval":false},{"sender":"bbudge@chromium.org","recipients":["dmichael@chromium.org","bbudge@chromium.org","teravest@chromium.org","chromium-reviews@chromium.org","yusukes+watch@chromium.org","raymes+watch@chromium.org","jam@chromium.org","yzshen+watch@chromium.org","joi+watch-content@chromium.org","darin-cc@chromium.org","sbc@chromium.org","piman+watch@chromium.org","binji@chromium.org","ihf+watch@chromium.org"],"text":"It seems kind of heavy weight. Could we get the same effect if we just checked in the host for 'Dev' permissions before clearing the write flags?","disapproval":false,"date":"2013-09-06 01:03:29.358450","approval":false},{"sender":"dmichael@chromium.org","recipients":["dmichael@chromium.org","bbudge@chromium.org","teravest@chromium.org","chromium-reviews@chromium.org","yusukes+watch@chromium.org","raymes